# Hero: sage war cockpit (~10s) with selection movement.
Output ../assets/demo-war.gif
Output build/demo-war.txt
Set Width 1200
Set Height 640
Hide
Type "export PATH=$HOME/bin:$PATH" Enter
Type "clear" Enter
Show
Type "sage war"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
Down
Sleep 600ms
Down
Sleep 600ms
Up
Sleep 600ms
Down
Sleep 800ms
Sleep 2s
Type "q"
Sleep 500ms
